 *
 *   - GND  = EXIO D pin 3, 4, 7, 8, 12, 17, 18, 45, 46, 54, 58, 63
 *   - CS#  = EXIO D pin 69
 *   - SCK  = EXIO D pin 71
 *   - MISO = EXIO D pin 65
 *   - MOSI = EXIO D pin 67
